posting_body: ['The Groves', '10811 SE 239th Pl, Kent, WA, 98031', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 127', 'Live in Spacious Kent, Wa Apartment Homes.', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 905 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Part of you loves quiet mornings on the deck, tranquil walks through the trees and a soak in the sparkling pools.', "A part of you craves action and excitement from the state-of-the art fitness center with indoor activity hub, outdoor basketball court and picnic area with barbecue's.", 'All that you want, all that you love; put together piece by piece, to create the ideal place to live.', 'Features', '- Walk-In Closets', '- Disposal', '- Window Coverings', '- Microwave', '- Office', '- Kitchen', '- High Speed Internet Access', '- Cable Ready', '- Refrigerator', 'Community Amenities', '- Covered Parking Available', '- Modern Clubhouse w/ Lounge Area and TV', '- State of the Art Fitness Center w/ Indoor Activity Center', '- Business Center', 'w/ High Speed Internet', '- Fenced Dog Park w/ Seating Area', '- Basketball Court', '- BBQ/Picnic Area', '- Multi-Use Sports Court and Playground', '- On-Site Laundry Facility', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Tuesday & Thursday:10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Sunday:12:00PM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Dogs and Cats Allowed.', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', 'HU7i4Vx7Xnp']
